This is the beginning of a requirements document for the ADR project.


The system/s should:

Be able to be used for both prisoner and non-prisoner ADR tracking.

Capture information needed by courts to evaluate and improve their ADR processes.

Provide a way for courts to report the newly required ADR statistics to the AO.

The system/s must be suitable for both small and large courts.

The system/s must require little to no maintenance once complete.
